snippet.title: Winter Survival Simulator New Trailer
snippet.description:
Please add WSS to your wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394960/Winter_Survival_Simulator/

A new video for Winter Survival Simulator showcasing a bit of the mood in the game for you to enjoy. All footage is from the current demo build, so you can experience everything for yourself in the demo of the game that will launch on February 3rd in time for the Steam Game Festival.

#wintersurvivalsimulator #DRAGOentertainment #simulator #gameplay
